Subject: [PATCH 14/41] web-app: hide second-device (multidevice backup
 transfer) UI

iroh isn't included in the wasm build (doesn't work locally with
browsers yet), so backup transfer via QR/second-device can't function.
Hide the entry points: the welcome-screen 'add second device' button
and the settings 'Add Second Device' item.
